succeeded in reverting to the original name for historical reasons 
for amnesiacs there is nameless texas 
grim said the local postmaster exasperated by residents 
bickering over what to name their new crossroads community wrote 
authorities in washington a letter declaring let the place be 
nameless and be damned the post office dutifully obliged 
