gives other health care providers has already signed up about 20 
states upjohn which announced its plans more than three months 
later has signed up just maryland so far 
while the discounts could cost the participating companies a 
significant amount in the short run analysts say those losses 
could be more than made up over time if the companies win enough 
medicaid contracts 
